text.section:
Bonds issued under the provisions of this title are securities in which all of the following may legally and properly invest funds, including capital in their control or belonging to them:
Public officers and public agencies of the State and its political subdivisions;
Banks, trust companies, savings and loan associations, investment companies, and others carrying on a banking business;
Insurance companies and insurance associations and others carrying on an insurance business;
Administrators, executors, guardians, trustees, and other fiduciaries; and
All other persons.
